ygData.messageBody:
Please reply to this post saying if you want me to add a gigantic
amount of hacks to this group, as well as links, and more files to
the file archive, for I have realized that this is a cheating group,
but it is empty.

Please reply by sending me an email at xteam_leader@...

Please make sure that Vote is in the subject line.

If you want me to add hacks to this group, which I am already doing
with around 3 other groups and 1 site, well read the following.

Want:I would like you to add EQ hacks to EQCheats *name*.

Don't Want: I do not want you to add EQ hacks to EQCheats *name*.

Please include your yahoo ID that is in this group, and make sure
that the above is just like I said, or I will probably delete your
email.

I hope you all vote yes, I will have the 40'some hacks within a week
that won't get you banned from EverQuest if you follow the guidelines
that I set out for them, however, if you don't, you will get banned...

I will include a guideline file concerning the hacks, and it will
have the max for every hack if you vote yes.

The highest vote within 3 weeks, you can only vote once, will win.

If you would like to change your vote for some reason, please include
in the heading, Change Vote, and I will change your vote. If you have
any questions, please email me at the email I have giving above with
the subject line being, Hack EQCheats, included with the question as
well, and I will try and reply as soon as I can.

I will need all votes within 2 weeks, I will have all the hacks in 1
week, but after two weeks, I will start deleting all questions,
votes, and other such things concerning it.
